trans-unit.source: The SoapHeaderMapping class represents a SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: SoapHeaderMapping 类表示 SOAP 标头映射。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref:System.Boolean> value that indicates whether the SOAP header mapping is custom-defined.
trans-unit.target: 获取<xref:System.Boolean>值，该值指示是否自定义 SOAP 标头映射。</xref:System.Boolean>
